Arpeggiate the long last chord with eg: 4 instruments sharing 3 notes,
to allow breaths.

    |uuuuu ddddd |uuuuu ddddd |uuuuu ddddd | 3 instr, 2 voices, cycle 12
    |ddd uuuuu dd|ddd uuuuu dd|ddd uuuuu dd|
    |u ddddd uuuu|u ddddd uuuu|u ddddd uuuu|

    |uu dd uu dd uu dd |
    |d uu dd uu dd uu d|
    | dd uu dd uu dd uu|
   
    |aaaa bb cc dd |
    |dd aaaa bb cc |
    |cc dd aaaa bb |
    |bb cc dd aaaa |
    |a bb cc dd aa |  :-(

    |aaaa bbbccc |  4 instruments, 3 voices, cycle of 12 beats
    |cc aaaa bbbc|
    |bbccc aaaa b|
    |a bbbccc aaa|

